welcome all,
this file will work as a guide for you about this project.


1) there is a class named 'modal' -> which should be invisible at start
    and as soon as the user click on '+' symbol it should be visible with an overlay effect with background as blurred.


2) in the container containing the notes only 4 notes should be seen in one row.
    and new notes should be pushed to the next row


3) the website is to completely responsive

